t of references and further bibliographical notes are added. Furthermore, there is an index. This grammar is the first accessible and comprehensive description of a Mosetenan language.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aMoseten languagexGrammar. 4aLateinamerika. 4aSprachen. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Reference.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Reference Works 2000-2014 (EN)z978311023850108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDe Gruyter Mouton Backlist 2000-2015z978311074296108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-DITION 2: BEST OF LINGUISTICS TITLES IN ENGLISHz9783110305616oZDB-23-DBH0 cprintz978311018340540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311091528040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110915280423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110915280/original  a978-3-11-023850-1  DGBA Backlist Reference Works 2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  a978-3-11-074296-1  De Gruyter Mouton Backlist 2000-2015c2000d2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DBH  aZDB-23-DLSc2000d2014